@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_qtiemz(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = wp.cos(((v1 + 0.03 * tmp + 0.90) * v2))
    v0 = 0.74
    v2 = v1
    v0 = wp.exp(wp.sin((tmp + 0.69 - v1 + 0.94)))
    data[tid] = v0
